{"notes":[{"midi":0,"start":3.38,"dur":5.7,"lyric":"I found a love for me"},{"midi":0,"start":9.08,"dur":9.2,"lyric":"Oh, darling, just dive right in and follow my lead"},{"midi":0,"start":18.24,"dur":6.8,"lyric":"Well, I found a girl, beautiful and sweet"},{"midi":0,"start":25.07,"dur":7.1,"lyric":"Oh, I never knew you were the someone waitin' for me"},{"midi":0,"start":32.18,"dur":8.4,"lyric":"'Cause we were just kids when we fell in love, not knowin' what it was"},{"midi":0,"start":40.53,"dur":7.2,"lyric":"I will not give you up this time"},{"midi":0,"start":47.7,"dur":8,"lyric":"Oh, darling, just kiss me slow, your heart is all I own"},{"midi":0,"start":55.66,"dur":6.9,"lyric":"And in your eyes, you're holding mine"},{"midi":0,"start":62.58,"dur":11.2,"lyric":"Baby, I'm dancin' in the dark with you between my arms"},{"midi":0,"start":73.75,"dur":7,"lyric":"Barefoot on the grass while listenin' to our favourite song"},{"midi":0,"start":80.73,"dur":7.2,"lyric":"When you said you looked a mess, I whispered underneath my breath"},{"midi":0,"start":87.9,"dur":13.6,"lyric":"But you heard it, \"Darling, you look perfect tonight\""},{"midi":0,"start":101.48,"dur":7.1,"lyric":"Well, I found a woman, stronger than anyone I know"},{"midi":0,"start":108.54,"dur":7.7,"lyric":"She shares my dreams, I hope that someday, I'll share her home"},{"midi":0,"start":116.23,"dur":8.3,"lyric":"I found a love to carry more than just my secrets"},{"midi":0,"start":124.51,"dur":6.6,"lyric":"To carry love, to carry children of our own"},{"midi":0,"start":131.15,"dur":8.3,"lyric":"We are still kids, but we're so in love, fightin' against all odds"},{"midi":0,"start":139.44,"dur":6.8,"lyric":"I know we'll be alright this time"},{"midi":0,"start":146.27,"dur":7.7,"lyric":"Darling, just hold my hand, be my girl, I'll be your man"},{"midi":0,"start":153.96,"dur":6.7,"lyric":"I see my future in your eyes"},{"midi":0,"start":160.63,"dur":11.6,"lyric":"Oh, baby, I'm dancin' in the dark with you between my arms"},{"midi":0,"start":172.24,"dur":7.1,"lyric":"Barefoot on the grass while listenin' to our favourite song"},{"midi":0,"start":179.36,"dur":6,"lyric":"When I saw you in that dress, lookin' so beautiful"},{"midi":0,"start":185.34,"dur":14.5,"lyric":"I don't deserve this, darling, you look perfect tonight"},{"midi":0,"start":199.88,"dur":0.2,"lyric":"No, no, no"},{"midi":0,"start":200.09,"dur":7,"lyric":"Mm, oh"},{"midi":0,"start":207.09,"dur":10.1,"lyric":"Baby, I'm dancin' in the dark with you between my arms"},{"midi":0,"start":217.17,"dur":7.6,"lyric":"Barefoot on the grass while listenin' to our favourite song"},{"midi":0,"start":224.77,"dur":6.2,"lyric":"I have faith in what I see, now I know I have met"},{"midi":0,"start":230.96,"dur":7.2,"lyric":"An angel in person, and she looks perfect"},{"midi":0,"start":238.18,"dur":6.6,"lyric":"Though I don't deserve this, you look perfect tonight"}],"melody":[{"midi":49,"start":3.03,"dur":0.09},{"midi":53,"start":3.25,"dur":0.3},{"midi":56,"start":3.58,"dur":1.52},{"midi":57,"start":5.1,"dur":0.41},{"midi":58,"start":5.5,"dur":0.13},{"midi":57,"start":5.63,"dur":0.1},{"midi":56,"start":5.74,"dur":0.42},{"midi":58,"start":6.18,"dur":0.09},{"midi":60,"start":6.29,"dur":0.2},{"midi":58,"start":6.5,"dur":0.17},{"midi":60,"start":6.7,"dur":0.16},{"midi":58,"start":6.87,"dur":0.09},{"midi":55,"start":7,"dur":0.09},{"midi":56,"start":7.09,"dur":0.19},{"midi":58,"start":7.29,"dur":0.19},{"midi":60,"start":7.49,"dur":2.09},{"midi":58,"start":10.52,"dur":0.29},{"midi":60,"start":10.82,"dur":0.86},{"midi":56,"start":11.8,"dur":1.5},{"midi":56,"start":14.29,"dur":0.27},{"midi":58,"start":14.56,"dur":0.43},{"midi":60,"start":14.99,"dur":0.17},{"midi":58,"start":15.17,"dur":0.99},{"midi":60,"start":16.16,"dur":0.1},{"midi":58,"start":16.27,"dur":0.49},{"midi":59,"start":16.75,"dur":0.26},{"midi":63,"start":17.11,"dur":0.38},{"midi":62,"start":17.5,"dur":0.1},{"midi":61,"start":17.6,"dur":0.1},{"midi":60,"start":17.71,"dur